    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Roman pottery that was widespread in the ancient world, characterized by a gray or brownish-gray base and a relatively simple design; often produced in small workshops.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
